    to keep building your brand.

09:44.917 --> 09:46.419
Yeah, but if I keep
         building my brand,

09:46.460 --> 09:49.046
I won't have any time
        to focus on my craft.

09:49.088 --> 09:50.798
There are a lot of big stars
         who haven't worked

09:50.840 --> 09:52.174
on their craft in years.

09:52.216 --> 09:54.969
-I know; I can tell.

09:55.011 --> 09:56.762
Trust me. You're a star.

10:01.058 --> 10:03.603
hip-hop music

10:03.644 --> 10:05.938
