Here we go.

10:12.695 --> 10:13.904
Ooh, let's take a selfie.

10:13.946 --> 10:15.740
-All right.
               -Okay.

10:18.117 --> 10:19.785
-Me.

10:19.827 --> 10:21.996
Okay.

10:27.043 --> 10:28.461
They love you.

10:30.671 --> 10:31.797
Hmm?

10:33.215 --> 10:37.553
So it's basically
         a movie about joy.

10:37.595 --> 10:38.804
That sounds amazing.

10:38.846 --> 10:43.017
Yeah, it'll feature people
       doing positive things.

10:43.059 --> 10:45.770
-Nice!
