10:45.811 --> 10:46.771
Ooh!

10:46.812 --> 10:49.523
Looking up the sky
     and laughing for no reason.

10:49.565 --> 10:52.026
At the end,
       everyone goes to space,

10:52.068 --> 10:53.986
and they fight evil aliens.

10:56.113 --> 10:58.532
Wow! That sounds...interesting.

10:58.574 --> 11:00.242
Well, it's still early days,

11:00.284 --> 11:02.411
-but my bosses love the concept.
            -Okay.

11:02.453 --> 11:03.746
Yeah.
     Marie hates it, of course.

11:03.788 --> 11:05.998
